  "description": "Dense grain cloud with slight pitch randomization per grain (pitchScatter=2.5 semitones) and a slow 0.067Hz position LFO sweeping through source material. The oscillator is a Two-Osc configuration with subtle detune. The result is a chorus of voices that has never been a vocal recording — the human in the machine without the human.",
